The paper focuses on video captioning, which involves both computer vision and natural language processing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a language model for captioning, which suggests that it could belong to cs.CL (Computation and Language). Additionally, the paper uses deep learning techniques, which could place it in cs.MM (Multimedia). The paper also mentions the benefits of the proposed approach, which suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper involves adaptive learning, which could place it in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
